# Cursor Rules for Tailwind CSS Project

## Project Context
This is a Next.js monorepo project using Tailwind CSS v3.4.1 for styling.

## Tailwind CSS
- Use Tailwind CSS classes for styling components
- Common patterns: className="bg-blue-500 text-white p-4 rounded-lg"
- Use responsive prefixes: sm:, md:, lg:, xl:
- Use hover/focus states: hover:bg-blue-600 focus:ring-2

## File Structure
- apps/user-app/ - Main user application
- apps/merchant-app/ - Merchant application  
- packages/ui/ - Shared UI components
- packages/db/ - Database package with Prisma

## Coding Style
- Use TypeScript for all components
- Use Tailwind CSS for styling (no custom CSS unless necessary)
- Follow Next.js 14 App Router patterns
- Use proper TypeScript types for all props and state 